title: State Street's Yie-Hsin Hung Speaks to BTV at Davos
description: State Street Investment Management CEO Yie-Hsin Hung speaks to Bloomberg TV’s Lisa Abramowicz on the sidelines of the 2026 World Economic Forum in Davos, Switzerland. (Source: Bloomberg)
